DungeonA fun 3-level adventure.The story:You were an American Tourist visiting Germany. When America joined the Allies, you were captured and brought to a horrible Prison. At least you were spared the Concentration Camp. A year ago you tried to escape. You were caught just outside your heavily-guarded cell. They tought you  Not to try that again. But now as you overhear the guards saying that Hitler himself is visiting, you wonder if another jail break would be a good idea. The guards are the scum of the Axis army; you shouldn't have much trouble killing them, because now you have a pistol...Miguel Fariascooter_31210@yahoo.com